ants for indoor use, in m<span><sup>3</sup></span>/yr.<p>W<span><sub>ref_occ</sub></span> \tis GSAS benchmark for the water demand of the occupants for indoor use for a specific building type, in m<span><sup>3</sup></span>/yr.<p><br/>The <span>criterion level</span> is established based on the result of the WPC<span><sub>dem</sub></span>.</p>")
